## 1. EXECUTIVE SUMMARY\par
\par
This document provides complete engineering specifications for the Auric Replicator Proof of Concept, a device designed to achieve Topological Resonance Lock at 148.5 kHz within a 1.0-inch hexagonal aperture, creating an "Active-Silence" condition for gold (atomic number 79) manifestation as described in the referenced patents.\par
\par
The documentation spans three distinct performance tiers:\par
\par
| Tier | Configuration | Cost | Relative Performance |\par
|------|--------------|------|---------------------|\par
| **Baseline** | As specified in patents | $450 | 1\'d7 (reference) |\par
| **Optimized** | Advanced components & controls | $1,200 | 10\'d7 |\par
| **Ultimate** | Cryogenic + quantum sensing | $34,000 | 10\'b9\f1\u8309?\f0\'d7 |\par
\par
All specifications are provided in both Imperial and Metric units with 4-decimal precision where applicable.\par
